title: The Ragged Canteen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Beer/Wine, English
description: Cafe and gallery. Offers changing menu of vegetarian lunches from 12-2:30pm with vegan and gluten free options, and Saturday is brunch all day. Relaxed environment with free Wi-Fi, magazines, weekend newspapers. Children welcome. During gallery hours, it serves cake and coffee from a vintage Italian espresso machine.
